<h1>Google AI Overview Stats 2026: CTR Drops and Recovery Data</h1>
<p><strong>Last updated: May 2026</strong></p>
<p>Organic click-through rates collapsed when Google AI Overviews expanded across search results in 2025. Then something unexpected happened in early 2026: CTR began climbing back. This post compiles the latest data from studies covering 2.43 billion impressions, 300,000 keywords, and 68,000 tracked searches to show exactly what changed — and what it means for your traffic.</p>
